T*
(- Economics and Incentives) Tj
T*
(Atho uses scheduled rewards with fee participation and long-tail issuance behavior. Economic) Tj
T*
(goals are predictable issuance, transparent accounting, and sustained miner incentives.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Emission and burn monitors compare expected and observed supply behavior to detect drift early.) Tj
T*
(- Threat Model and Defenses) Tj
T*
(Atho defends at three layers.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Protocol layer:) Tj
T*
(- strict signature and UTXO checks,) Tj
T*
(- coinbase and fee enforcement,) Tj
T*
(- block linkage and target validation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Network layer:) Tj
T*
(- mempool policy controls,) Tj
T*
(- peer visibility and node telemetry,) Tj
T*
(- deterministic payload handling.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Operational layer:) Tj
T*
(- wallet lock/unlock controls,) Tj
T*
(- API credential/HMAC support,) Tj
T*
(- role-pinned API routing to reduce stale endpoint confusion.) Tj
T*
(- Operations and Governance Direction) Tj
T*
(Atho favors explicit operations over hidden automation:) Tj
T*
(- clear start/stop/restart/switch behavior,) Tj
T*
(- persistent runtime configuration,) Tj
T*
(- structured logs for incident audit and recovery.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Governance direction is engineering-led: improve safety, correctness, and observability before) Tj
T*
(expanding protocol complexity.) Tj
T*
(- Roadmap Priorities) Tj
T*
(- Continue role-isolation hardening across node, wallet, GUI, and explorer.) Tj
T*
(- Expand mempool and peer policy depth under adversarial conditions.) Tj
T*
(- Improve key-management UX while preserving strict security defaults.) Tj
T*
(- Improve diagnostics and explorer drill-down for faster audits.) Tj
T*
(- Increase automated coverage for consensus, reorg, and high-volume transaction edges.) Tj
T*
(- Conclusion) Tj
T*
(Atho is built to address real operating pain: stale state surfaces, unclear role boundaries,) Tj
T*
(payout drift risk, and weak observability. The long-term goal is a resilient network where) Tj
T*
(protocol integrity and operator usability improve together.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
